      <title>研究显示，由于欧洲投资担忧，中国收购量下降</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/study-shows-dip-chinese-takeovers-amid-european-investment-concerns-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[审计和咨询公司安永的一项研究显示，中国面临的经济挑战，加上对中国在欧洲投资的谨慎态度，导致去年中国买家在欧洲大陆的收购数量下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/study-shows-dip-chinese-takeovers-amid-european-investment-concerns-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 10:30:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度动力煤进口量自大流行以来首次下降</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-thermal-coal-imports-seen-falling-first-time-since-pandemic-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[行业官员周二表示，由于国内产量增加和库存创历史新高，预计今年印度动力煤进口量将出现自 COVID-19 大流行以来的首次下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-thermal-coal-imports-seen-falling-first-time-since-pandemic-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 10:18:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿里巴巴旗下南亚电商巨头Daraz在备忘录中宣布裁员</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/alibabas-south-asian-e-commerce-giant-daraz-announces-layoffs-memo-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿里巴巴旗下的电子商务平台 Daraz Group 代理首席执行官 James Dong 周二在路透社看到的一份致员工的内部备忘录中表示，该公司已宣布在整个集团进行裁员，以“采用更加精简和灵活的结构”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/alibabas-south-asian-e-commerce-giant-daraz-announces-layoffs-memo-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 06:49:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>牙科种植体制造商士卓曼对 2024 年持谨慎态度，押注中国增长</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/dental-implants-maker-straumann-sees-steady-sales-growth-2024-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士种植牙制造商士卓曼 (Straumann) 周二预测 2024 年销售额将稳定增长，在长期的经济不确定性中采取谨慎立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/dental-implants-maker-straumann-sees-steady-sales-growth-2024-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 06:47:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着中国出货量激增，印度四月至一月钢铁进口量创六年新高</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-apr-jan-steel-imports-six-year-high-china-shipments-surge-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透社周二看到的临时政府数据显示，在中国出货量的带动下，印度钢铁进口量在截至3月份的本财年前10个月触及六年来新高，并且印度是成品钢材的净进口国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-apr-jan-steel-imports-six-year-high-china-shipments-surge-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 06:43:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚贸易部长表示，中国葡萄酒争端可能在几周内得到解决</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-wine-dispute-may-be-resolved-weeks-australian-trade-minister-says-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚贸易部长唐·法雷尔周二表示，与中国有关澳大利亚葡萄酒关税的贸易争端可能“在几周内”得到解决，从而消除了限制其对华出口的最后障碍之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-wine-dispute-may-be-resolved-weeks-australian-trade-minister-says-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 06:11:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南计划进行工会改革以避免贸易困境，但冒着外国公司不安的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/vietnam-plans-union-reform-avert-trade-woes-risking-foreign-firms-unease-2024-02-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国官员和外交官表示，共产党统治下的越南预计将在今年批准联合国自由建立工会公约，此举旨在降低贸易争端风险，但可能会让一些外国公司感到不安。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/vietnam-plans-union-reform-avert-trade-woes-risking-foreign-firms-unease-2024-02-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 04:04:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
